rather err on the side of caution.

216
00:16:39,995 --> 00:16:43,632
[sighs] I understand,
but I don't know who to call.

217
00:16:43,699 --> 00:16:45,801
Well, look, there is a detective
who's quite good,

218
00:16:45,868 --> 00:16:47,170
who I can recommend.

219
00:16:47,236 --> 00:16:49,472
Although,

220
00:16:49,538 --> 00:16:51,373
right now, you haven't received
your inheritance yet.

221
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:55,478
Is there, uh... would you be able
to afford this?

222
00:16:55,544 --> 00:16:57,180
If available,
I'll have him call you,

223
00:16:57,246 --> 00:16:59,315
and perhaps you can both work
something out in deferment.

224
00:16:59,381 --> 00:17:00,483
How's that?

225
00:17:00,549 --> 00:17:02,485
Okay.
Thank you.

226
00:17:02,551 --> 00:17:03,586
Thank you.

227
