It's your house.

250
00:18:29,605 --> 00:18:31,640
[suspenseful music]

251
00:18:46,655 --> 00:18:48,357
Your photo journal fell down.

252
00:18:55,332 --> 00:18:58,601
[chuckles]
We were such troublemakers.

253
00:19:06,209 --> 00:19:07,610
Well, you were.

254
00:19:07,676 --> 00:19:09,578
