1172
01:22:25,274 --> 01:22:26,809
[panting]

1173
01:22:35,152 --> 01:22:36,318
[disembodied voice]
You see it?

1174
01:22:40,456 --> 01:22:41,657
Take it.

1175
01:22:43,492 --> 01:22:44,827
You see it?

1176
01:22:45,861 --> 01:22:47,196
Take it.

1177
01:22:56,173 --> 01:22:57,573
Feel it.

1178
01:22:57,640 --> 01:22:59,775
[eerie music]

1179
01:23:31,373 --> 01:23:33,909
Shh.

1180
01:23:41,383 --> 01:23:42,485
