1181
01:23:45,855 --> 01:23:47,289
Come on, nuh-uh, nuh-uh.

1182
01:23:47,356 --> 01:23:49,992
You know what lies
in this room, huh?

1183
01:23:50,059 --> 01:23:54,396
Uncle Fun isn't having fun anymore
