Come here.

1185
01:23:56,732 --> 01:23:58,334
All right. All right.
Careful now,

1186
01:23:58,400 --> 01:24:00,669
careful,
you don't want to cut yourself.

1187
01:24:00,736 --> 01:24:01,837
[Lily] No!

1188
01:24:01,904 --> 01:24:03,873
Uh-uh, uh-uh, uh-uh, come here.

1189
01:24:03,939 --> 01:24:06,575
All right, and our next exhibit,

1190
01:24:06,642 --> 01:24:08,677
Aunt Naggie hanging
from the curtain rod.

1191
01:24:08,744 --> 01:24:12,014
- No, no, no! No!
- Uh-uh, uh-uh-uh, come here. Ready for this one?

1192
01:24:12,081 --> 01:24:15,218
Bend down. Here we go.
