1193
01:24:15,284 --> 01:24:18,587
Look at that.
Oh, poor Sharksdale,

1194
01:24:18,654 --> 01:24:21,023
[chuckles]
shot in the head.

1195
01:24:21,090 --> 01:24:22,958
Let's go to the next one.
Come on.

1196
01:24:24,527 --> 01:24:26,362
All right. Come on.

1197
01:24:26,428 --> 01:24:28,531
[grunts] Here we go.

1198
01:24:28,597 --> 01:24:30,167
Your dear friend Amber.

1199
01:24:33,236 --> 01:24:34,271
Suffocated.

