01:24:35,738 --> 01:24:36,772
Let's go.

1201
01:24:38,241 --> 01:24:40,210
- [Lily grunts]
- [grunts]

1202
01:24:40,277 --> 01:24:45,381
I'll just tell you this one,
Bonkers' drink poisoned.

1203
01:24:45,447 --> 01:24:47,616
Please don't do this.
Let me go.

1204
01:24:47,683 --> 01:24:50,085
Uh-uh, uh-uh, uh-uh-uh. Let's go to
the bedroom, shall we, for the finale?

1205
01:24:50,153 --> 01:24:51,854
Come on.

1206
01:24:51,921 --> 01:24:54,890
Walk up the stairs.
There you go.

1207
01:24:54,957 --> 01:24:56,458
You got it.

1208
01:24:56,525 --> 01:24:59,262
That's it, you're going to take
a nice right.

1209
01:24:59,328 --> 01:25:00,496
There you go.

